From: Vlad Lungu <vlad.lungu@windriver.com>
Date: Tue, 15 May 2012 17:43:15 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 212/628] Xilinx: ARM: SPI: Allow OF configuration of SPI
 devices

git://github.com/Xilinx/linux-xlnx.git xilinx-v14.7
commit 15d9c8e44673258a975c45c8832333d0e26e8069

A minor update to the driver.

Signed-off-by: Vlad Lungu <vlad.lungu@windriver.com>
Signed-off-by: Liming Wang <liming.wang@windriver.com>
---
 drivers/spi/spi-xilinx-ps.c |    1 +
 1 files changed, 1 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/drivers/spi/spi-xilinx-ps.c b/drivers/spi/spi-xilinx-ps.c
index 31061be..4ec3997 100644
--- a/drivers/spi/spi-xilinx-ps.c
+++ b/drivers/spi/spi-xilinx-ps.c
@@ -654,6 +654,7 @@ static int __devinit xspips_probe(struct platform_device *dev)
 		return -ENOMEM;
 
 	xspi = spi_master_get_devdata(master);
+	master->dev.of_node = dev->dev.of_node;
 	platform_set_drvdata(dev, master);
 
 #ifndef CONFIG_OF
